      "content": "\"let go of the struggle\" ... i dont know. it just feels like there isn't even a struggle anymore, just this heavy, empty feeling. like, if the outcome is already decided for us, then every single breath we take is just delaying the inevitable. it's exhausting to keep pretending like there's a way out or like we can actually change anything. it feels more logical to just... stop fighting it, you know?",
